Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運氣也是推理的關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的事情也能看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的故事發生在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連句會上的罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.90,0:00:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻智慧過人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.80,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.79,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something' just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.96,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,在追尋著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.48,0:00:26.69,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣了謊言 現在也一樣 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.71,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.21,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,一切毫無定數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.23,0:00:41.28,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,即使一個人也不能哭泣軟弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.57,0:00:51.06,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,與真實的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.55,0:00:59.87,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 映射出來 朝著兩個人所決定的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.50,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.87,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,朝著沒有盡頭的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.23,0:01:13.21,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.50,0:01:18.22,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah.You're going nowhere .It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.49,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,切實地前行著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.78,0:01:28.83,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,感受現在 You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.92,0:01:32.87,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋季的某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去島根縣松江旅遊的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.60,0:01:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在松江溫泉遇到連句會的5個會員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.00,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5人中的牛漥剛三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在松江城的游步道上被殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右手食指指著某個方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是什麼死亡留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人十有八九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那四個人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連句會決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.30,0:02:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,松江玉造連句十四次勝負(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始連句會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一共有14句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是連句14
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.70,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓初學者毛利先生也能參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用文字接龍的規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是文字接龍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要遵守一點規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.40,0:02:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要從和樹木有關的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二句就要很快地說出一個兇猛的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再請說出一個平常都能用到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:03:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後從14句當中加入旬和佳節等數句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中間加入關於月亮的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的兩三句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第13句是關於花的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後的結尾句以春天愉快收場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做做試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先說發句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家說說自己作的句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾神也 聚來觀賞啊 鹿之窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木澤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大龜旁 螳螂把斧頭 高高揚起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搖曳的楓樹 朝向日光的方向 紅葉飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有牛漥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋高氣爽 我的人生裡 沒有憂愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作的都很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次為了祭奠牛漥的亡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用他的那句作發句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼誰來作肋句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是肋句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是第二句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.40,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和發句有同樣的韻 還要有標點符號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寂靜之中 木實落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著是八木澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸能作出來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月光明亮 然後就來了吸血鬼 湊上一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.10,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼這個兇猛的人物很有新意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個也行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三句脫口而出就很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始跟著自己的想像走就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著想像走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講義 是日本製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按韻不如說課本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然簡單了一點 不過沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在輪到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接上一個字尾是h的句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把犯人 抓給你們看 就是名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很新奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.80,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探的世界和吸血鬼的世界很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點跳句的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過挺好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面該我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此行的目的是 發現神的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是禮子老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探的積極態度被一揮而散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼簡單的可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,類人猿 臉長得很像 鄰居的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第7字「我」是重點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在大廳撿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是傻瓜 又丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家很厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.80,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.80,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下3句了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還找不出來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最開始你作的關於紅葉的連句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說是坐在武家故居的休息場上根據看見的景色而作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我去了武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在休息場是看不見紅葉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是在其它的地方看見的紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉是犯人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要撒謊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒準就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉是為了那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣也解釋不了牛漥死時留下的信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個人為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生讓我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.20,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說讓背著安來警探幫忙查查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒弄錯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人很可能就是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛漥死的時候要告訴我們的信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的手指不是指著竹子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是指著竹子前面的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.90,0:09:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿過游步道直指崛川對面的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是美杉去看紅葉的武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個第10句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是愛情的句子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是單相思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木澤昨天晚飯的時候點過眼藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.50,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉單相思的是八木澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以美杉昨晚就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛漥對八木澤說話很不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉看見了很為八木澤擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉 你是不是在掩護八木澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.40,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉昨晚聽見牛漥和八木澤的談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是就改變了計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去松江城見了牛漥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡美杉看見的卻是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒看見那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實話實說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨口就說出來了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的喜歡什麼人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的為他著想的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來要去的不是松江城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是月照寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很為八木澤擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.20,0:11:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是中途碰巧看見去松江城的公共汽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看見八木澤也在車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻跟著去了松江城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是等我到達游步道的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛漥已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後那個手指指向的方向…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我急忙回到武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在休息場平靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到了該回來的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就回到了旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實去了松江城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我沒殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒去游步道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你去了松江城的哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稻荷神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個有很多狐狸像的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他叫我去那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是牛漥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到達月照寺後30分鐘左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛漥突然給我發了短信來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻到松江城的稻荷神社來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我10點5分左右到達神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那裡等了大約15分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛漥沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給他打電話也沒有回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 我就回到月照寺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作了大龜的那句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你的眼藥水會掉在現場呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我說的都是真的 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是覺得我說謊了 請去看看牛漥的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手機的履歷已經都查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.40,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有給你發過短信的履歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預備的手機查了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛漥說在包裡還預備了一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的東西都檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手機只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.40,0:13:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你偷了牛漥的預備手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後給自己發的短信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安來警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶器找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扔在月照寺的噴水池裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特製警棍用雨衣包著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面沾著的血液和被害人的血型一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個雨衣上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是鐵證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我回警察局問話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.20,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都覺得是個誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一句讓我說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開頭字母是Q吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力糖果 快給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是連句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從螞蟻的道聯想到的巧克力糖果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子式的可愛的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一句是花的句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎名 你說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.20,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 開頭字母是I
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說個好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 女兒和我兩個人 花的寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.30,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這句和剛才毛利叔叔給我念的那句一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.70,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸什麼時候作的這麼一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.10,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這句確實不是我作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.10,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天在大廳裡遇到的浪花證券的友永作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後牛漥把它記在手冊上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.70,0:16:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定以為是牛漥作的句子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為那樣差勁的人怎能作出這麼漂亮的句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果就從手冊上撕下了那一頁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你把牛漥殺害之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.80,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在你自己的連句裡面夾著暗語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第7句的第7字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第9句的第9字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第11句的第11字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是對我寫下的挑釁的那句的報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接在自己的句裡面加上信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑警察和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷樂著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照你的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為只要有條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就一定會把從牛漥那裡偷來的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.70,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說成是自己所作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這句是你非常喜歡的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡富有感情色彩的句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親思念女兒那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是八木澤作為犯人被帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及第13句花的句的第一個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和前面那句的結尾發音一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說柯南剛才說的那句是爸爸讓他說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我推理的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把從牛漥那裡偷來的句子念出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是給自己慶祝勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連句的暗語只是惡作劇而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那句是昨晚牛漥給我看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我有不在現場的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在現場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10點5分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.10,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在庭院美術館的英國庭院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.00,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看見一個迷路的孩子被交到他父母手裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才才想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情裝個攝影機就能辦到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝在灌木叢的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南在客人散去後找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上你到了庭院美術館之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在灌木叢下面安裝了攝影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.40,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用偷來的牛漥的備用手機給八木澤發了短信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後去松江城殺害了牛漥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:19:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又把八木澤的眼藥水放在牛漥的手指前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在月照寺扔掉雨衣和凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去庭院美術館拿回攝影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.40,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就若無其事地回到旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的推理 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有證據的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛漥死之前給我們留下的死亡留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那既不是指著竹子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是指數字「１」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連句的第一句是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.10,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椿警探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑒定結果怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.30,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這雙登山鞋左腳左側最上面的鉤子邊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了牛漥沾著血的右手手指的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:19:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.90,0:20:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是想說你的鞋子的鉤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我推測你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光注意到牛漥的手冊裡的句子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒注意他摸了你的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是我殺了牛漥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.30,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼覺得我奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最初讓我感到奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚抽籤的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常做簽的人最後才抽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你卻是第二個抽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面按照年齡來抽 該我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時你在簽上作了手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓牛漥抽到了容易作案的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己則抽到最遠最容易做不在現場證明的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是日本第一的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺害牛漥的動機果然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:21:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙了我們的錢 怎麼能饒過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 你也沒有權利裁決他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.60,0:21:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠裁判他的只有神明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是神明為了讓我明白這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才讓你來到這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:41.08,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然等待著刺激的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.61,0:21:47.72,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,但最重要的還是眼前的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.98,0:22:00.27,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕會失去什麼 但我們手中並沒有掌握什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.77,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.90,0:22:07.61,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,在這蔚藍的地球上 重複著無限的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.87,0:22:12.85,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,can make me free 就好想感受這樣的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.94,0:22:14.28,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.41,0:22:20.06,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺輕舞飛揚 在天空和大海之間烙上痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.31,0:22:29.86,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊地將你抱入懷中 想展翅高飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.00,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.16,0:22:38.88,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺輕舞飛揚 在天空和大海之間烙上痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.17,0:22:48.52,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊地將你抱入懷中 想展翅高飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.60,0:22:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉的心意八木澤好像明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.40,0:23:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 禮子老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.00,0:23:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連句還剩一句沒完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.40,0:23:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了表達對毛利的感謝之情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有對松江的喜愛之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.20,0:23:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫卡狄歐漢 微笑的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.40,0:23:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.10,0:23:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.30,0:23:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫卡什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.20,0:23:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫卡狄歐漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.00,0:23:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是小泉八雲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小泉八…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.50,0:23:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是"拉夫卡狄歐漢 睏倦的春天"啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.10,0:23:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何小偷要偷這個破廟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要偷大筆善款的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊看上去也沒有許多捐款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.70,0:24:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.20,0:24:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.60,0:24:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以證明小偷非去帝丹神社的理由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.90,0:24:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.20,0:24:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世間奇妙的天罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.90,0:24:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.40,0:24:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捐贈箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.60,0:24:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集是出人意表的迷案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 爸爸的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.30,0:24:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天譴啊
